      <title>html学习笔记</title>
      <link href="/2024/04/05/html%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
      <url>/2024/04/05/html%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="学习html的笔记（图片后续系统性补充吧）"><a href="#学习html的笔记（图片后续系统性补充吧）" class="headerlink" title="学习html的笔记（图片后续系统性补充吧）"></a>学习html的笔记（图片后续系统性补充吧）</h1><h1 id="第一天"><a href="#第一天" class="headerlink" title="第一天"></a>第一天</h1><p>html的标签分为单标签和双标签</p><p>双标签一般都是包裹内容的包括但不限于文本</p><p><strong>文本</strong>这个是加粗文本用的标签</p><hr>这个标签可以产生出一条横线<p>html的基本骨架</p><p>最前和最后分别需要有<html> </html></p><head>网页的头部，用来放给浏览器看的代码。比如css<p><tittle>标签存在于<head>标签里。用来显示网站的标题的</p><body>网页的主体，用来存放给用户看的代码，包括但不限于文字和图片<p>在vscode里  英文输入法状态下按!和enter或tab键可实现一键生成基本骨架</p><p>标签的关系</p><p>1：父子关系（嵌套关系）</p><p>2：兄弟关系（并列关系)</p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/6de7dd02-f21b-4d0c-84bc-c75698ae048d/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p>比如 这里的<html></html>里面包裹的都是属于他的子关系，<head>和<body>既是兄弟关系</p><p>缩进控制快捷键tab为向前缩进&#x2F;shift+tab为向后缩近</p><p>vs中注释可以用ctrl+&#x2F;</p><p>h1到h6对应不同级别的标题</p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/5f59bc6c-7080-4b46-9de4-9b0d7621207e/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p>段落<p>内容</p></p><p>单标签</p><p><br>换行</p><hr>水平线<p>：</p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/b3c68f50-e50f-4571-9744-87112e5d6d58/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p>图片标签</p><p><img>单标签 它的属性src的作用是指定图像的位置名称或者链接 alt是对图片的描述 当图片无法加载是就会显示alt的描述</p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/ecbba6df-8280-4d47-aabb-1b9c9b8a0d30/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/b78e2338-0fc1-42df-88e7-2a4f2cb8aaa8/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p>高度和宽度非必须。可用css定义</p><p>超链接标签</p><p><a> href&#x3D;”这里填跳转的链接 target&#x3D;_blank(作用是新开一个·窗口打开所跳转的网页·”</a> herf&#x3D;#的话表示空链接 并不会进行跳转</p><p>音频标签</p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/7a1b74d7-5280-4b28-bc59-6ba432638c27/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p>视频标签</p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/1f1dd6b1-e26f-4f35-82c4-0ff7d835b3ba/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p>注解：如果想要在浏览器中实现视频的自动播放 则必须要有muted值</p><p>4.4学习结果</p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/7f34cf67-5e80-4df8-8d7f-3eb4c8aff786/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/3ff39d84-14ac-4b3c-bf3c-6ba812137cf2/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><h1 id="第二天"><a href="#第二天" class="headerlink" title="第二天"></a>第二天</h1><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/a2395e5e-6392-43cf-88a5-2130ee54692f/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p>ul标签里面只能包裹li标签 不限制li标签的数量 且li标签里面可以放任何内容</p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/466a910b-0489-4c52-96f2-dfa5648f5426/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/4a8ec4d7-281c-45e2-b97e-b41fe169c416/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/360e3840-fda8-4f3e-a947-425f8f7f27d7/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/d3756252-6790-4dcf-b81e-c13d2e77a487/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/f648521f-6f43-440d-a246-e59b827ff785/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/bca7eb9c-f322-4cf1-9b64-b33d9231d3a4/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/d7866dd4-5c67-490c-b342-f71aa397d04a/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/1e1c3cc2-3d3d-4da4-a2f6-ab5fd30b744a/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/3d446aa2-1f19-44de-8dc1-3f35c7341585/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p>checked默认选择</p><p>name&#x3D;“”可分类别才会实现单选功能</p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/10702d98-d34c-4a58-a127-6a632c8ae384/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/18d31b8d-2388-4127-9cab-edcb7b91f976/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/4a55f1af-0992-4955-a88b-bec368edb170/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/03e15d87-cb09-41e5-ba9d-a212208fb532/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p>需要用<form></form>包裹内容。比如</p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/c9dc65ac-d43d-4ce7-8e4a-6a84826e4936/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/84452e92-c351-4348-bf46-07ffe586a250/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p><img src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/f088ce1e-f3f5-4f25-9cb5-c8f64cead9d5/cc6a6f8a-0fbb-47fa-ae23-238f9d2d0f42/Untitled.png" alt="Untitled"></p><p>字符实体用来在网页中显示&lt;或者&gt;或者空格 因为<or>在html中会被看作是标签。空格的话在编辑器中无论敲多少空格都只会被识别为一个 所以是很有必要的</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
